    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Polygun, an endlessly customizable hero shooter where you battle against an ever increasing hoard of bloodthirsty shapes! With an array of upgrades to choose from, you'll quickly build from humble beginings into a hexa-bustin killing machine.  The possibilities are endless! How long can you survive?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your hero!  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/715dd4815482753eb3cefcd19bae23e3.poster.avif?t=1764447273\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/715dd4815482753eb3cefcd19bae23e3.webm?t=1764447273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/715dd4815482753eb3cefcd19bae23e3.mp4?t=1764447273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from among a variety of eye-catching heroes with unique weapons and ability focuses!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gain experience and unlock new upgrades!  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/d6a37393f85a0aa437db10804676b917.poster.avif?t=1764447273\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/d6a37393f85a0aa437db10804676b917.webm?t=1764447273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/d6a37393f85a0aa437db10804676b917.mp4?t=1764447273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new levels of power by vanquishing foes and spend your hard-won experience points to transform your character into an unstoppable force!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your game!  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/1c342e86b08ad42a4fd8ca03279f2184.poster.avif?t=1764447273\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/1c342e86b08ad42a4fd8ca03279f2184.webm?t=1764447273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173480/extras/1c342e86b08ad42a4fd8ca03279f2184.mp4?t=1764447273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polygun has full customizability, from editing color palettes, and creating new heroes, to custom upgrades and difficulties, you can tailor the perfect Polygun for you!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
